;   - Functional vs imperative comparison + tradeoffs
;   - Writing imperatively in a functional language (set!, boxes,
;     state monads)
;   - Implementing an imperative language IN Scheme
;   - Implementing a declarative language IN Scheme
;   - Database internals (relational algebra, query planner, indexing)
;   - Type inference (Hindley-Milner)
;   - Metacircular evaluator (Scheme in Scheme)
;   - Language paradigm comparison
